        <p class="blog-title">Embracing the Freelance Lifestyle: Unlocking a World of Professional and Personal Benefits<p>
        <p class="blog-date">Dec 7, 2017<p>
        <div class="fakeimg">
          <img class="blog-image" src="images/top-blog-2.jpg" alt="freelancing">
